Test case # 1
Summary: Sign up for OurApp button with valid values in Username, Email and Password fields.

Preconditions:
1. The website https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/  is opened.
2. The user with the name anbondarenko isn’t registered.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Enter “anbondarenko” to the Username field.
2. Enter “anbondarenko@mailinator.com” to the Email field.
3. Enter “111111111111” to the Password field.
4. Click on the button Sign up for OurApp.

Expected result:
There is the next text on the page: “Hello anbondarenko, your feed is empty. Your feed displays the latest posts from the people you follow. If you don’t have any friends to follow that’s okay; you can use the “Search” feature in the top menu bar to find content written by people with similar interests and then follow them.”


Test case # 2
Summary: Create Post button.

Preconditions:
1. The website https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/  is opened.
2. The user with the name anbondarenko is registered.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Enter “anbondarenko” to the Username field.
2. Enter “111111111111” to the Password field.
3. Click on the button Sign in.
4. Click on the button Create Post.

Expected result:
There are on the page: “Title” field, “Body Content” field, “This is a unique post” checkbox, “Select value” drop-down menu, “Save New Post” button.


Test case # 3
Summary:  Sign in button with empty Username and Password fields.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Go to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/.
2. Click on the button Sign in.

Expected result:
There is an Error message on the page.


Test case # 4
Summary: Save New Post button with empty “Title” field.

Preconditions:
1. The website https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/  is opened.
2. The user with the name anbondarenko is already signed in.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Click on the button Create Post.
2. Enter some text and symbols to Body Content field, for example, Test543@.
3. Click on Save New Post button.

Expected result:
1. There is pop-up message near Title field – “Заполните это поле”.
2. The post wasn’t saved.


Test case # 5
Summary: Sign Out button.

Preconditions:
1. The website https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/  is opened.
2. The user with the name anbondarenko is already signed in.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Click on the button Sign Out.

Expected result:
1. There are Sign in and Sign up for OurApp buttons on the page.
2. The user was signed out.
